{"tid":878047,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Pepper會係娜美星同Thanos隻揪]《復仇者4》Pepper著新裝甲救Tony Stark？","createTime":"2018-10-26T21:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T15:09:22.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"682a4d6053a4cd3273ef5ddb1675350348d112a9","tid":878047,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T21:07:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=27603&amp;catid=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D27603%26catid%3D21&d=zCJ0UJg2t9OPWjHovkihfP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=cd2984ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=27603&amp;catid=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrcd8Qd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyrcd8Qd.jpg&h=3e4253e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTony Stark女友Pepper Potts喺《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》內出場只得短短數十秒，不過下一集似乎會有更多發揮機會。近日有一張「Pepper」Gwyneth Paltrow身穿裝甲嘅照片流出，證實新英雄Rescue將會誕生。<br />\n<br />\n照片中嘅裝甲以紫、銀為主色，與Marvel動畫中嘅Rescue Armor用色相近。故事中Rescue Armor由Tony Stark製作，擁有跟Iron Man裝甲相近嘅作戰能力，系統更特別加入隱身模式及變聲器，確保能夠隱藏Pepper本人嘅真正身分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5KLZXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5KLZXe.jpg&h=5a9c7b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:ComicBookMovie<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.comicbookmovie.com/avengers/avengers_4/avengers-4-a-first-look-at-gwyneth-paltrow-suited-up-as-rescue-has-leaked-online-a164298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comicbookmovie.com%2Favengers%2Favengers_4%2Favengers-4-a-first-look-at-gwyneth-paltrow-suited-up-as-rescue-has-leaked-online-a164298&d=zCJ0UJg2t9OPWjHovkihfP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=ab19de36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.comicbookmovie.com/avengers/avengers_4/avengers-4-a-first-look-at-gwyneth-paltrow-suited-up-as-rescue-has-leaked-online-a164298</a